{"tid":41384,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：朋友告訴我，特朗普用了我的政治理論、戰略思想、社交網絡傳播風格","createTime":"2016-12-16T00:39:45.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-16T04:54:24.000Z","uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c4795efd5ff9e6d031837c20f0c113c6f53f9e27","tid":41384,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T00:39:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0igft47o\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0igft47o&h=28701141&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳雲：我有生以來，在香港經歷過越戰、文革、土共暴動、石油危機、金融風暴、六四屠殺、九七過渡，有些在香港爆發，有些由大陸發動，但我從未見過這麼令人畏懼的美國總統上台。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>（朋友告訴我，特朗普用了我的政治理論、戰略思想、社交網絡傳播風格，甚至在網台節目的身體語言。美國用雷動計劃摧毀我的議席和政治反擊能力，之後加碼抄襲我的戰略。我遇到我自己，而且是超級國家的實力加強版，這是最令我最畏懼之處。）<br />\n</strong></span>"},{"pid":"7fd2696f7389e7590a65b7cf6477018912476ba9","tid":41384,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T00:43:09.000Z","msg":"韋拿踢法似我"},{"pid":"6c5d9fefbc6355e244c801cca6312b7d29f3c039","tid":41384,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T00:43:34.000Z","msg":"係香港點經歷到越戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91d69856e608470cf36f7dcbf6a5159ff92250fe","tid":41384,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T00:44:41.000Z","msg":"皇天擊殺普普, 死全家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfe3fca2d2eeed51871717a253730dee6c53a486","tid":41384,"uid":23947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T00:46:32.000Z","msg":"朋友靠訴我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你朋友便是你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fc693be48d867d049f5f0cc182fd6dfab271223","tid":41384,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T00:47:13.000Z","msg":"當日陳韋